ca.uqac.lif.labpal.table

Class Table

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.uqac.lif.labpal.table.Table
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataOwner
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DataTable, ExperimentTable, TransformedTable, VersusTable

    public abstract class Table
extends Object
implements DataOwner
    A multi-dimensional array of values. Tables can be passed to Plot objects to generate graphics.

      • getTypeOf

        public static Class<? extends Comparable<?>> getTypeOf(Object o)
        Guess the type of a column in a table, by looking at the type of one of its values. The type is defined as follows:
        • Any JsonNumber and any Number will return Float
        • A JsonList will return its own type
        • A null object returns null
        • Anything else returns String
        Parameters:
        o - The value to look at
        Returns:
        The type
